{"type":"app","meta":{"headers":{"x-nextjs-stale-time":"300","x-nextjs-prerender":"1","x-next-cache-tags":"_N_T_/layout,_N_T_/legal/layout,_N_T_/legal/[slug]/layout,_N_T_/legal/[slug]/page,_N_T_/legal/privacy"},"segmentPaths":["/_tree","/_full","/legal/$d$slug/__PAGE__","/legal/$d$slug","/legal","/_index","/_head"]},"html":"<!DOCTYPE html><html lang=\"en\"><head><meta charSet=\"utf-8\"/><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\"/><link rel=\"preload\" href=\"/logo.png\" as=\"image\"/><link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/_next/static/css/53ebd3f615d9682f.css\" data-precedence=\"next\"/><link rel=\"preload\" as=\"script\" fetchPriority=\"low\" href=\"/_next/static/chunks/webpack-4c9e6c08dcc7a301.js\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/4bd1b696-215e5051988c3dde.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/794-4d0b7b700451cc43.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/main-app-c7dc77e60f3b3e6e.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/app/layout-ec2df61e02bf9503.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/500-c99b8dfd3de17c86.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/app/legal/%5Bslug%5D/page-15bc5f6386411560.js\" async=\"\"></script><link rel=\"preload\" href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fraunces:ital,opsz,wght@0,9..144,300;0,9..144,400;1,9..144,300;1,9..144,400&amp;family=Geist:wght@300;400;500;600;700&amp;display=swap\" as=\"style\"/><link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com\"/><link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://fonts.gstatic.com\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\"/><meta name=\"theme-color\" content=\"#0A1120\"/><title>Privacy Policy | Client Era</title><meta name=\"description\" content=\"How Client Era collects, uses, and protects your business and operational data.\"/><meta name=\"author\" content=\"ClientEra\"/><link rel=\"manifest\" href=\"/manifest.webmanifest\"/><meta name=\"keywords\" content=\"CRM,sales software,field sales,commercial OS,AI sales platform,pipeline management,sales intelligence\"/><meta name=\"creator\" content=\"ClientEra\"/><meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow\"/><link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https://clientera.aio/legal/privacy\"/><meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"Privacy Policy | Client Era\"/><meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"How Client Era collects, uses, and protects your business and operational data.\"/><meta property=\"og:url\" content=\"https://clientera.aio/legal/privacy\"/><meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"article\"/><meta name=\"twitter:card\" content=\"summary_large_image\"/><meta name=\"twitter:title\" content=\"ClientEra — The Unified Commercial OS\"/><meta name=\"twitter:description\" content=\"One platform for your entire commercial relationship — from the first conversation to the last payment.\"/><meta name=\"twitter:image\" content=\"https://www.clientera/logo.png\"/><link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/favicon.ico?603d046c9a6fdfbb\" type=\"image/x-icon\" sizes=\"16x16\"/><link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/logo.png\"/><link rel=\"apple-touch-icon\" href=\"/logo.png\"/><link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fraunces:ital,opsz,wght@0,9..144,300;0,9..144,400;1,9..144,300;1,9..144,400&amp;family=Geist:wght@300;400;500;600;700&amp;display=swap\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/polyfills-42372ed130431b0a.js\" noModule=\"\"></script></head><body><div hidden=\"\"><!--$--><!--/$--></div><main style=\"background:var(--navy);min-height:100vh;color:var(--text);display:flex;flex-direction:column\"><header style=\"width:100%;padding:24px clamp(24px, 5vw, 64px);border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;position:sticky;top:0;z-index:100;backdrop-filter:blur(10px);background:rgba(11,22,40,0.85)\"><a style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;text-decoration:none\" href=\"/\"><img src=\"/logo.png\" alt=\"Client Era Logo\" width=\"120\" height=\"32\" style=\"object-fit:contain\"/></a><div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:24px\"><a style=\"color:var(--text2);font-size:13px;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1px\" href=\"/legal\">Legal Center</a><a class=\"lh-btn\" style=\"padding:8px 16px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.05);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);border-radius:8px;color:var(--text);font-size:13px;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none;transition:all 0.2s\" href=\"/\">Return to Site</a><style>\n          .lh-btn:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1) !important; }\n        </style></div></header><div style=\"flex:1;max-width:860px;margin:0 auto;padding:64px 24px;width:100%\"><article class=\"legal-content\"><h1>Client Era Privacy Policy</h1>\n<p><strong>Last Updated: March 2026</strong></p>\n<p>Client Era (&quot;we,&quot; &quot;us,&quot; or &quot;our&quot;) operates the clientera.com B2B operations and distributor management platform. This Privacy Policy details how we handle the personal and corporate data we collect when you use our platform.</p>\n<h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>\n<h3>A. Operational Data</h3>\n<p>Because we are a B2B platform, the primary data we collect is related to supply chain and operational efficiency:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Corporate Contact Info:</strong> Names, email addresses, and phone numbers of authorized users (distributors, sales managers, dispatchers).</li>\n<li><strong>Transactional Records:</strong> Sales orders (SORs), proforma invoices, pricing agreements, and fulfillment tracking logs.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>B. Technical Data</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>IP addresses, browser types, and device identifiers required to secure the platform.</li>\n<li>System activity logs, session durations, and interaction metrics used to optimize platform functionality.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>2. How We Use Information</h2>\n<p>Client Era processes data to:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Authenticate authorized users and enforce role-based access controls across our modules.</li>\n<li>Facilitate B2B commerce (e.g., executing SORs, notifying distributors of ETA updates).</li>\n<li>Maintain service security, prevent fraud, and maintain comprehensive audit trails.</li>\n<li>Analyze operational bottlenecks to improve our software routing and algorithms.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>3. Data Sharing and Sub-processors</h2>\n<p>We do not sell operational or personal data to third parties. We only share information with:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Sub-processors:</strong> Essential infrastructure providers (e.g., AWS, Vercel) bound by strict data processing agreements.</li>\n<li><strong>Your Organization:</strong> Actions performed by users (e.g., a Sales Manager) are visible to authorized personnel within the same organization based on defined permissions.</li>\n<li><strong>Legal Compliance:</strong> Law enforcement or regulatory bodies, only when legally required.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>4. Data Security</h2>\n<p>Client Era employs enterprise-grade security, including:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Encryption of data in transit (TLS 1.3) and at rest (AES-256).</li>\n<li>Strict infrastructure access controls and role-based operational permissions.</li>\n<li>Regular vulnerability scanning and independent security audits.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>5. Your Rights</h2>\n<p>Depending on your jurisdiction, you or your organization may have the right to:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Access, rectify, or erase your personal operational data.</li>\n<li>Withdraw consent for non-essential data processing.</li>\n<li>Request an export of your transaction history.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>To exercise these rights, please contact your organization&#39;s Platform Administrator or email us at <strong><a href=\"mailto:privacy@clientera.com\">privacy@clientera.com</a></strong>.</p>\n</article></div><footer class=\"ce-footer\"><div class=\"ce-footer-grid\"><div><div class=\"ce-footer-logo\">client<em>era</em></div><p class=\"ce-footer-desc\">The AI-Powered Commercial Operating System. One timeline. One truth. Zero gaps.</p><p style=\"font-size:11px;color:var(--text3);margin-top:14px\">Built for India. Compliant worldwide.</p></div><div><div class=\"ce-fc-h\">Platform</div><ul class=\"ce-fc-links\"><li><a href=\"/sales-ops\">Sales Ops</a></li><li><a href=\"/sales-management\">Management</a></li><li><a href=\"/customer-support\">Customer Support</a></li><li><a href=\"#\">Field Sales</a></li><li><a href=\"#\">Desk Sales</a></li><li><a href=\"#\">Operations</a></li><li><a href=\"#\">Distributor Portal</a></li></ul></div><div><div class=\"ce-fc-h\">Company</div><ul class=\"ce-fc-links\"><li><a href=\"#\">About</a></li><li><a href=\"#\">Security</a></li><li><a href=\"/faq\">FAQ</a></li><li><a href=\"#\">Pricing</a></li><li><a href=\"#\">Careers</a></li><li><a href=\"#\">Blog</a></li></ul></div><div><div class=\"ce-fc-h\">Legal</div><ul class=\"ce-fc-links\"><li><a href=\"/legal\">Legal Center</a></li><li><a href=\"/legal/privacy\">Privacy Policy</a></li><li><a href=\"/legal/terms\">Terms of Service</a></li><li><a href=\"/legal/cookies\">Cookie Policy</a></li><li><button style=\"background:none;border:none;padding:0;color:inherit;font:inherit;cursor:pointer;text-align:left\">Cookie Preferences</button></li></ul></div></div><div class=\"ce-footer-bottom\"><span>© 2026 ClientEra. All rights reserved.</span><div class=\"ce-footer-links-row\"><a href=\"/legal/privacy\">Privacy</a><a href=\"/legal/terms\">Terms</a><a href=\"/legal/cookies\">Cookies</a></div></div></footer></main><!--$--><!--/$--><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/webpack-4c9e6c08dcc7a301.js\" id=\"_R_\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"1:\\\"$Sreact.fragment\\\"\\n2:I[7121,[],\\\"\\\"]\\n3:I[4581,[],\\\"\\\"]\\n4:I[9351,[\\\"177\\\",\\\"static/chunks/app/layout-ec2df61e02bf9503.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n6:I[484,[],\\\"OutletBoundary\\\"]\\n7:\\\"$Sreact.suspense\\\"\\na:I[484,[],\\\"ViewportBoundary\\\"]\\nc:I[484,[],\\\"MetadataBoundary\\\"]\\n